                    <h1 class="display-3">Alive by Google</h1>
                    <p class="lead">Alive by Google is a website to appreciate all the wonderful work, applications, services, etc we only have because of Google</p>
                    <hr class="my-2">
                    <p>Once you actually stand still. Think about things. Think about the things that you use, have used or will use. In the IT but even outside this "niche" - Google has been a fundament for a lot of things. Not just the plain obvious stuff, such as Google Search. There is so much more to discover. </p>
                    <p>This website is actual free (no ads nor tracking), contains no javascript and is open-source. Everyone is allowed to contribute.</p>          
					
					<h2>Contributing</h2>
					<p>Feel free to drop by <a href="https://github.com/wiardvanrij/Alive-By-Google">GitHub</a> and create a Pull Request.
					This way you are able to add entries and be involved in the development of this website.
					</p>
