                <div class="col-sm-6">
                    <h2 class="display">Created because...</h2>
                    <p class="lead">It's easier to point out failures or mistakes rather than appricate the things we actually have.</p>
                    <p>This website is made as counter for "killedbygoogle". A fair website/list, yet focusses on <b>only</b> the negative part. As someone as myself, I have used so many Google products. I honestly believe they deserve better than a graveyard.</p>   
                    <h2>The goal</h2>
                    <p>Eventually the goal is to inform and provide an equal sound of the positive side. Not to bash, hate or attack "killedbygoogle". Everyone should have the right to express their thoughts, opinion, whatnot. </p>
                    <p><i>This also means it's okay to use Google Analytics on your "KilledbyGoogle" website. hehe.</i></p>
